  <summary date="2017-04-06T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Recognizes the 100th anniversary of the 1st Infantry Division.

Commends such division for continuing to exemplify its motto, "No Mission Too Difficult. No Sacrifice Too Great. Duty First!"

Honors the memory of the more than 13,000 soldiers of the division who lost their lives in battle.</summary>
